			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~Aaden42">Aaden42</a>  <span class="uid"><a href="//slashdot.org/~Aaden42">(198257)</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_44904303">		
		on Friday September 20, 2013 @12:50PM (<span class="ind"></span><a href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=4241059&amp;cid=44904303">#44904303</a>)
		<small><a href="http://www.iphonebookshelf.com/" title="http://www.iphonebookshelf.com/" class="user_homepage_display">Homepage</a> </small>
